{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"FormData.getAll()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\">XMLHttpRequest</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/FormData\"><code>FormData()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>append()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/delete\"><code>delete()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/entries\"><code>entries()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><em><code>getAll()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/has\"><code>has()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/keys\"><code>keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/set\"><code>set()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/values\"><code>values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ähnliche Seiten zu XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die&nbsp;<code><strong>getAll()</strong></code> Methode der&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a> Schnittstelle gibt alle Werte zurück, die innerhalb eines&nbsp;<code>FormData</code> Objekts&nbsp;mit einem gegebenen Schlüssel assoziiert sind.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Hinweis</strong>: Diese Methode ist in&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a>&nbsp;verfügbar.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"append_parameters","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"name\"><code>name</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein <a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_9094f63a1f7efd350dd69d6a8ae174fb\"><code>USVString</code></a>, der den Namen des Schlüssels darstellt, der abgerufen werden soll.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"rückgabewerte","title":"Rückgabewerte","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Ein Array von <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormDataEntryValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>s.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Die folgende Zeile erstellt ein leeres <code>FormData</code> Objekt:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> formData <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">FormData</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Hinzufügen von zwei&nbsp;<code>username</code> Werten mit Hilfe von&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/append\"><code>FormData.append</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Chris'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nformData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">append</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Bob'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Der darauffolgende Aufruf der&nbsp;<code>getAll()</code> Funktion gibt beide <code>username</code> Werte in einem Array zurück.:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>formData<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'username'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// gibt [\"Chris\", \"Bob\"] zurück</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikation","title":"Spezifikation","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-formdata-getall\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XMLHttpRequest<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'getAll()' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.FormData.getAll","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHTTPRequest</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\" title=\"Using XMLHttpRequest\">Using XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData/Using_FormData_Objects\" title=\"DOM/XMLHttpRequest/FormData/Using_FormData_objects\">Using FormData objects</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/form\"><code>&lt;form&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikation","id":"spezifikation"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"Die getAll() Methode der  FormData Schnittstelle gibt alle Werte zurück, die innerhalb eines FormData Objekts mit einem gegebenen Schlüssel assoziiert sind.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FormData.getAll()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/formdata/getall","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/formdata/getall/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData","title":"FormData"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/FormData/getAll","title":"FormData.getAll()"}],"pageTitle":"FormData.getAll() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}